{"tid":1168722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"悚！7歲女童陪老爸加油　身上靜電瞬間引火焚身","createTime":"2019-05-24T01:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T09:19:34.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"736a9af5220fdac072f9f300400174167da2338a","tid":1168722,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:21:18.000Z","msg":"自助加油時務必當心身上的靜電啊！墨西哥一對父女日前到加油站，7歲女兒就站在汽車油箱旁看著爸爸加油，豈知「轟」一聲突然竄出大火，爸爸心急之下抽出油槍，汽油頓時漫天噴灑，火勢一發不可收拾。<br />\n墨西哥《El Universal》21日報導，這起加油站火警事故發生在克雷塔羅聖地亞哥（Santiago de Quer&eacute;taro）。從監視器畫面可看到，就在7歲女童靠向油箱的一瞬間火勢被引燃，推測是她身上的靜電所致。<br />\n加油站人員緊急拿滅火器撲滅火勢，將被火吞噬的父女送醫，兩人身上雖有多處一、二級燒傷，但幸好未危及生命。醫師表示，非常慶幸小女孩的傷勢不重，她應該幾天後就能出院。<br />\n提醒民眾，加油前務必先釋放身上的靜電！據粉絲專頁《119消防聯網》資訊，防止靜電有4點須注意：<br />\n1. 加油前先放電，下車後用手觸摸金屬物或者牆壁，都可以將身上的靜電釋放。<br />\n2. 加油過程中不要回到車內，否則身上會再次被附上靜電。<br />\n3. 加油前最好將加油槍在油箱口輕碰一下，以消除靜電。另外，加油時應將油槍儘量的深入油箱內，這樣可以減少汽油的揮發，降低危險。<br />\n4. 加完油不要馬上拔出加油槍，避免油槍頭上還有殘餘的油滴，如果遇到火星會引起火災。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190524/640_b4d38a77281d92095332c6b713a72a52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190524%2F640_b4d38a77281d92095332c6b713a72a52.jpg&h=9cadcf51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190524/1572092/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190524%2F1572092%2F&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhKjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=59ca9299\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190524%2F1572092%2F&h=4600694a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190524/1572092/</a>"},{"pid":"42d04cd6d7178a6d81bbc1eee622686690574e54","tid":1168722,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591680fa979458340346720de949a867b32afacf","tid":1168722,"uid":243669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:25:11.000Z","msg":"好彩傷勢不重"},{"pid":"177ece5531e18aa6a0f2e60f399d36de254c1c87","tid":1168722,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"591680fa979458340346720de949a867b32afacf","tid":1168722,"uid":243669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:25:11.000Z","msg":"好彩傷勢不重"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T08:54:10.000Z","msg":"不過痛都痛死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2131e42e611a0665145432052120d9bb22e4c836","tid":1168722,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T09:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fac09872d039a3b09b656bd697f092d6630d095","tid":1168722,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T09:19:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}